### Academic Integrity:

All students are accountable for academic integrity, according to the standards described in the academic handbook.

Standards regarding citation/plagiarism are also available online. See especially the kinds of plagiarism (direct plagiarism, the mosaic, paraphrase, and insufficient acknowledgment) and how to avoid them or fix them: [http://www.northwestern.edu/provost/policies/academic-integrity/how-to-avoid-plagiarism.html][rlnu]

[rlnu]: http://www.northwestern.edu/provost/policies/academic-integrity/how-to-avoid-plagiarism.html
